values: Well no one reads this anyway but shana and evelyn, and I tell them everything any way so I don't really see a point in keeping this journal anymore. I'm just going to make one for myself. So goodbye shana and evelyn haha.

<b>Yesterday Me and shana and some of my family Drove all the way to riverside to watch Star Wars 3 at the drive-in movie theatre. It was fuckin awesome. Me and shana laid on the ground and ate pizza while we watched the movie. Thats the best way to watch it. The movie got over at like 11 and it was an hour long drive back to long beach to drop off shana and a 30 min dive back to downey, so of course my mom was really tired and she started to fall asleep on the road. We almost crashed it was actually pretty funny for some reason. Yup so obviously if I'm updating my journal at at 11:30 on a monday I didn't go to school, So there goes my 3 week streak of not missing school.
     Movie Tickets: $15
     Pizza and soda: $15
     Gas: $34
     Watching star wars with friend and hearing your aunt yell "oh no! Yogurt!" when yoda falls: Priceless

Haha that was pretty funny. Last night really was great.

<b>Right now I'm at shanas house having an awesome time. Andy was here earlier but he left at like 5. Dude he fucking kicks ass at guitar, I'm so  freakin' jelous. Yup right now were watching the 100 greatest rock moments. 
Ya it was weird cause I called my mom and she was just like "I got your guitars in the car with your amp and some clothes and a 2 liter and i called shana and I'm taking you to shanas house." I was just like ok. Haha ya I opened my soda and when I opened it everything was fine but then it just started going everywhere and shana was just sitting there laughing her ass off. Ya she said I started yelling for help. It was great. Well I'm sure shana prolly wants me to get off so I'm out.

<b>Well I got my progress report. Who is else is in trouble? haha. This was my worst report card in my whole life. I've never did this bad. Lets just say my highest grade was a D and I only recieved 1 of those. I thought my mom was going to kill me when I showed it to hear but sje was chill about it. I think she was high or something because obviously she wasn't acting herself. Usually I wouldbe cowering in fear as she yelled and took all my "privledges" away but she just told me to do better. I was very confused. I still kinda am.
     Somethings been wrong with me lately. I know evelyns noticed because everyday at school she keeps poking me and asking me whats wrong because she says I look like I'm going to cry and for those of you who know me, I don't cry. None of my friends have ever seen me cry. Nicole had the privledge of hearing me cry over the phone once though haha and she was scared. But ya theres seriously something wrong and I don't know what! I guess I'm just lonely or something. I have my friends and I'm grateful for them because theyre the best group of friends I could ever ask for but sometimes that just doesn't seem to be enough. 
    Ok well thats enough of my complaining. I've been starting to play guitar again becuase I went awhile without playing but its great playing again, music has always been my one emotional outlet. I'm tying to learn a black sabbath song and a metallica song right now, theyre both coming along great. Well I really don't know what else to say so I'll talk to you cool kids later.

P.S. Pray for Dannys(singer of NP) brother Dave who was in a bombing accident while in Iraq fighting a war that we shouldn't be fighting. Hes in critical condition.

<b>Normally I would say my life sucks but it doesn't. I'm just so fricken bored! Everday is repetitive. I get up, get dressed, go to school, meet friends for nutrition, go back to park ave., meet friends on C-side for lunch, go to class, and if its an even day I go to shanas which is always fun or if its odd I go to another class, then go home, then do nothing, then go to bed and wake up and it all starts again. This has been going on almost all month and at first I liked it because I knew what to do and where to go and I like being organized but now its just boring. I mean I love spending time with my friends,thats not the problem at all I just feel like I'm missing something. I want an exciting new change in my life but I don't what to do. I know it probley seems like I'm complaining but this is really botherig me. I honestly have no idea what to do.

Well I didn't go to school today because I had a doctors appointment and that lasted forever. After that me and my mom decided to go down 4th street and check out the stores. We went to the little shop called Roadside Room and they had a sweatshirt in there that I wanted (i'ma go back for it :D). We also got Erics hair cut a few hops away from there and he looks like a pimp now. Then we decided we wanted some coffee and there was this little coffee place not to far called Portfollio (I think thats what it was called) and so we went there and I really liked it. Its a kinda place where you could just chill, I think I'll go back again sometime. After that we went to the $1 movies and saw MAn Of The House it was pretty funny. Thats all I did today, it was pretty fun. I got some new pants!!! I was so happy cause I've been wanting new jeans for awhile.

On Saturday I went to Disney's California adventure with shana, we had fun but it was so freakin crowded and the people who work there are retarded or something because they were giving us problems all day. We were there for like 9 hours and only got to go on two rides, see one show and do one activity. But here are some pictures!!!!!
Haha we went to watch Aladin the musical and while we waited we compared our feet. Shanas feet are really small!
We went on the Tower of Terror, it was awesome!
You can't go to Disneyland without getting ears!
If you look closely you can see mine and shanas mickey ear shadows.
Its Goofy!!!

<b>This last week has sucked so bad. I got a ticket from school, yesterday me and Evelyn got picked up and taken to the Truancy center and because of that I have to go live with my Grandma for awhile. I was supposed to stay with her tonight but what happened you may ask? I woke up in a great deal of pain and my mom said she couldn't do anything about it because she had to go to school. So I spend a majority of the day in a lot of pain waiting for my mom to get home so I could go to the hospital. I go to the hospital and they run a bunch of fucking tests anfd keep me there for like 5 freakin hours but they still don't know whats wrong with me so they sent me home! What the fuck! They told me to come back if I become unconcious or the pain starts spreading to somewhere else. Why don't they try and help me now! why must I come back when its worse? They might as well just say come back when your dead! I'm still fucking hurting but theres nothing they can do. Arrg I hate hospitals.

Well I finally got my NP pictures uploaded, I know some of mine and shana's pictures look the same but mine are better. haha. So check them out.
I have like 140 picture but I'm not gonna post them all. I also have some hilarious videos but you have to come over to see those.

Well this is a picture of what my room looked like before. I'll post after pictures once its completely done. This was the only picture I had left after re-booting my computer so you can only see half of my room.If you look at the pictures on the wall you can see me and shana haha. ohhh and theres penguins in the corner haha. and the no smoking and no parking signs are ducked taped to my window becuase I broke it :) haha my medication is fucking me up.

<b>Today I went to the movies and saw Beauty Shop it was actually pretty funny. Other than that everything else pretty much sucked. I have a really bad headache and my strep throat seems to be getting worse, I think I'm dying but I'm not that lucky. Later I think I might actually get up off my lazy ass and finish painting the rest of my room. I have to or else I can't go to guitar center tommorrow. 

Earlier this morning me and my mom got in our first argument in monthes, she was the one who started it though. I was trying to be nice but she just kept on criticizing me so I started yelling at her, I think thats why my throat got worse and she could tell that my throat was hurting because I could hardly talk anymore so she tried to be nice but I was too pissed off so I broke my mic she got me (it was a toy one haha). Ya so to make up for it she took me to the movies. Yup well I'm gonna go paint now aka take a nap haha.

<b>Well I finally got my phone back so I can start going online more often. Theres been alot going on lately. On Monday I went to Knotts Berry Farm with shana which was a lot of fun. We had a couple of stalkers. On Thursday me and shana went to a national product show which was freakin awesome. I loved the part where danny's face was right up against mine and he was singing to me! lmfao haha sorry shana! 
Yup I havent gone to school in like 3 weeks but its not like anyone really noticed except evelyn. Shes such a good friend. Hmmmmm...what else....I'm also no longer on medication and everything is seems to be going fine so far. Ohhhhhhh i'm also re-decorating my room and looks awesome so far. I'll post pictures later, i'm too tired to right now.welp talk to you all later, even though the only person who will probley read this is shana.

<b>Well today I went to my job interview, I think it went pretty well. I really hope I get the job. I'm not going to tell anyone what it is unless I'm for sure I get the job. And no it's not at red lobster. Thats just my back up job if I don't get this one. Right now I'm at the library so thats how i'm using a computer. HOw come no one leaves me any damn messages! Leave me a message! please! hahaha. oh for anyone who doesn't know, Rick is in my 6th period class. I thought I didn't like him anymore (or at least thats what I told myself) but I was way wrong, but now that he's in my class I don't know what to do. Oh well I'll just play it "cool" hahaha lmfao. well thats all really. ttyl (if you leave me a message)

<b>Damn it's been so long since I've updated this damn thing. Well first off I'd like to thank angel for the Volvox demo I was listening to it earlier with shana and we both agree its fucking awesome. OK and I'm sad to report casey moved out yesterday but at least I get some of the stuff he left behind like the Xbox so thats cool. I havent really been up to anything lately but I'm proud of myself because I've gone to school for 3 week without missing a single class except evening school which I ditched last tuesday when I went to shanas house and my mom had no idea even though when she picked me up in jeans and a black t shirt. I also missed this tuesday. well thats all really so I guess I 'll update again when I can which sould be soon because we'll be getting our phone back pretty soon. Later Sucka Fish.

<b>Right now I'm at shana's house. Its been so long since I've been online. I don't even know what to write about. Not to mention its been awhile since I've been to school, so far I've only gone once this week. Nothings really been going on lately. My older brother Casey moved in with us along with his best friend Joey (he's so cute). And for those of you who don't know I've decided to give up on the whole rick thing because I never got a response so I just figured that the answer was a Hell no. Yup but now I'm thinking of taking EPHS this year because I'm starting to fall behind with all the school I've been missing. I havent been to my 2nd period class in almost 2 monthes. 
 Ya well thats all thats been going on. I have a boring life. Yup Yup Yup.

MY BIRTHDAY IS IN 5 DAYS. YAY!!!!!! I'LL BE 17!

<b>Today I ran away cause me and my mom had a fight so I took off and I walked like a mile to get to shanas. Yup but I'll eventually go back lol.
I wrote a note to nicole today and when I went to give it to nicole I noticed I didn't have it and it had a lot of personal infomation in it and later on today shana told me my graphic design teacher found it (she has him after me) and he read it in front of the whole class. That really sux.
Ooooh and yesterday at evening school there was like this new guy in the class and he kept starring at me and I was like what the hll is this guys problem then at the end of class he asked me for my number. I was like WTF? He must have made a mistake because I mean honestly just look at me! well Thats all thats been going on lately.

<b>Sorry I haven't been on in so long but my phone got disconnected. Right now I'm at shanas doing this. I can't believe shana just left school whats up with that? haha. OH for those of you who don't know I am officaly on anti depressents but I don't think they're working very well. Well anyways I've been kinda of annoyed lately because I want to know something but I don't know how to find out. hmmmmmm. Well anyways I'm gonna go for now and I'll try to update again as soon as I can.

<b>I think I did something really stupid today. I am so lame. For those of you who know what I did probley agree with me. If you don't know *cough cough evelyn* call me and I'll tell you.

Well I went to back to school night because I forgot all my room numbers and so my mom made me go so I could show her where they were. I got an F in english! I'm so smart haha. All my teachers (except english) had something good to say about me I was so suprised. I raised my D in science to a B in just 1 week so I'm really happy about that. Yup so everything is going OK so far in school at least.

OOOOO tommorow I get to go find out if I need Zoloft tommorow. If you see after school I'll tell you if I have to or not. haha. so evelyn I can't share.

Tommorows the NP concert!!! I finally finished my belt.

Today was alot better than yesterday. I slept in really late. I did some reasesrch on the Salem witch trials which is very intriguing. We are currently reading and watching the crucible in english class which I'm really interested in right now. So ya I'm just randomly trying to get more information on it because I can't wait till next class. Well I just finished watching "The boy in the plastic bubble" its been a long time since I've watched it that I forgot I bought it. But then I got pissed off at the end of the movie because I wanna know if he's gonna die for leaving his bubble. haha. well other than that nothing interesting has happened today. So thats all. I took a little nap and now I feel a better.

<b> I'm so fucking tired of everything! Everything in my life is so fucked up. I have so many fucking problems but then again who doesn't these days. I can't wait for so many fucking things to end so I can just fucking move on. Why do everything have to be so complecated. I need a break from this shit. Hopefully over this weekend I can clear my head and try to get things to go back to normal but the chances of that are highly unlikely. Fuck I'm so fucking angry that I can't even express it. I want to fucking scream. I think I'm just gonna get off for awhile and try to take my mind off things because I think being online is making it worse.

<b>I've been working on a song the last couple of day but I couldn't play it on my electric because I couldn't find my amp cord but I just found it and I played my song on it and it sounded ok but when I put it on distortion it sounded (as shana would say) bad ass. 
Oh I for got to mention I went to see my counsler the other day to se how many credits I was behind and it turns out I'm going to graduate on time and I'm only 5 credits behind which I'm already making up in evening school. I'm so proud of myself. haha. I can also still get my medallion. I just can't fail any classes from now on and maintain at least a 2.0.
<b>I'm sick and feel like shit! Blah! This fucking sucks. Today fucking sucked. Arggg.

<b>Yesterday - I went to a picnic which I thought was going to be really lame cause all I was going to was sit there which I did last year because its an annual picnic but this time I had an awesome time I was sad when it was all over. I think it was becasue this time I actually got involved and talked to people. I did the water balloon toss which we lost because my mom can't catch shit, and I played bingo (I was always one away from winning) and we had a water gun fight which was between me and this one guy because he randomly just started shooting me so I took my little brothers gun and shot back until we got yeld at because the old people were getting wet. I also did the cake walk and I was the first person to win so hahahaha to all those who didn't

Today - I got up early (11am that is early) and I went to the 99cent store and got some gum for school and some arizona iced tea (yummy but don't have both of them at the same time I learned the hard way) then I went to wal-mart and got the folder I needed for evening school and T-shirt for joey(my puppy) some other crap I can't remember and then we took my little joey to Pet co. to get his nails clipped and the guy that worked there was sOoOoOo freakin cute and his name was joey too haha. Then after that we went to the Elephant Bar which was awesome cause I've never been there before and ya it was awesome lol.

well thats all for now I got to do my homework.

<b>I go so long without updating that I don't talk about all the things that happen in my life that are interesting. So I'll try and remember them now.

Thursday Sept. 16 - It was the first day of practice which ok for a first day. I also had evening school and it was cool cause I met some knew people in that class and we had a really interesting conversation.

Sunday Sept. 19 - Me and Nicole went to raging waters. We had an awesome time until I got kidnapped haha ask me and I'll tell you about it.It was awesome because we got to ride there in one of those classic 50's cars.

Monday Sept. 20 - I went and ordered my glasses, and I found out we have to move because our landlord is a bitch.

Friday Sept. 24 (today)- I went to school which actually wasn't that bad at all and it was the first day I wore my glasses and I had interesting reaction when people saw me in them (Jose pointed and laughed). After school I had a doctors appointment to go get some tests done that my psychiatrist recommended to see if its ok for me to take zoloft or some shit like that cause he says I'm depressed. The blood test went fine (those fucking vampires taking my blood!) but I had no idea what an EKG test was so when the doctor told me I needed to take off my shirt I was like WTF?!? and ya I'm going to stop talking about that now. But anyways things have been going ok in my life for right now but I know that will change when it comes time to move which is going to suck ass because I finally have my room the way I like it. Oh well. Thats all for now.

<b>Today was my first day of evening school and it wasn't as bad as I thought it was going to be. I know a few people in my class and they give us a break so thats cool. Ya and thursday its a half day so we get out at like 5 instead of 6.
I had Unscheduled today but I had to wait in that long ass line for my sticker and I didn't get outa there until almost 2 and then I had to wait for my mom cause I told her to pick me up at 1:20 but snce I was waiting for my sticker and she didn't know that she took off and went to shanas casue she figured i was there which i wasn't. Then we went to a uniform store to get some stuff for eric and then we went to tower record to get my ticket but now I have to get $8 to go to randalls show at the allen theatre. I seriously need to get a job I need money badly. well I guess thats all for now. later.

<b>The NP show tonight was fucking awesome. Seriously it was the best show I ever went to. There was a lot of crazy shit going on. I don't know what the hell the guy with the needle was doing all I know was when he was lickin his blood of his arm that was fucking nasty. Oh and the dude that threw up the gold fish was fucking nasty too, I almost threw up. My favorite part was when danny was looking straight at me singing harbor and I was singing along with him that was fucking awesome. I wanted to talk to Rob after the show but I didn't see him. I can't wait for the next show. Shit my ears are still fucking ringing I can't hear shit. Well I'm fucking tired I was screaming and jumping around all night, so lateeer you Krazy Krackers.

P.S the bands that played are Delux, olivia, holloway, beyond conception, NHOI, and National Product or course.

<b>I changed my backround yet again but I really like it now so I think I might keep it now cause it's danny. I can't wait for the NP show tommorow night its going to be so awesome and we get their new cd its gonna be so great. I just hope we get there early cause if we don't we won't get close to the stage and that will really really suck.

On sunday Nikki wants me to go to Di Piazza to see Addie Bundren, I hope I can go.

Well that all for now I guess. I had written a longer entry but i got disconnected and it got erased so I'm just suming up what i wrote before.

P.S I finished school on tuesday and I got all A's. Yay for me.

<b> Today sucked really bad because I'm really sick and it hurts like hell to talk. I went to the mall today so Bryan could get some new shoes but the whole time I felt like I was going to pass out so we went home and I went to sleep for a little while.

Yesterday I went to EPHS and found out I passed english with an A so I'm really happy about that but then I had to go to my grandmas house after cause I needed a ride to practice. Yesterday was the last practice and it was a lot of fun. It was great getting to see nicole, eddie, jason, ramon, and everybody again.

I also started talking to this really nice guy named Joe recently. He is really cute and he has the sexiest voice on the phone. I called him the other night but no one needs to know what we talked about. Well I guess thats all thats been going on lately. Oh i forgot to mention I'm leaving on sunday. I'm going to Stockton but I'll be back on wednesday, I'll updat again when I get back.

<b>Yesterday was my second meeting with my therapist and she suggested that I see a psychiatrist to see if I should be on some kind of medication because I have trouble sleeping and she thinks I might be depressed. I also almost got kicked out of EPHS today becasue if you miss it 2 times they have to kick you out and i missed today but my teacher doesn't want to kick me out because I'm the only one out of her 60 students who have actually earned credits this summer and because I earned them so quickly that she thinks if I'm more dedicated I can earn the rest of them before EPHS closes which will be on august 13. So she wants me to come in tomorrow to take 3 tests and get a shit load of work to do cause I'm taking off on sunday to go to stockton to take bryan back home. So I'll miss my therapy session on monday so I have to call her and tell her I can't make it.

yesterday I finally went to the museum of tolerance after my therapy. It is an awesome museum. They did a mini model of Aushwitz. Plus they have you go through tunels that lead to gas chambers just like the jews had to do. It was so sad but bryan was being an ass becasue he doesn't really get what happened to the jews because he's a stupid ass jock. After we went to the museum we drove down Rodeo drive and stopped and asked some rich looking people in front of one of the stores where the nearest wal-mart was. It was funny as hell. then we went to hollyweird and then we went to downtown los angeles and went shopping. I got some nice shit down there and its so fucking cheap. well I gotta do i have homework to do.<b>

<b>Wow it's been almost a month since I've last posted. Casey and Bryan came to visit us on friday and we've been doing a lot stuff since they've been down. casey left today which was pretty sad but he'll miss out. On saturday we went shopping, Sunday we went to the movies, monday me, my brothers, my cousin and his friends, my parental unit, and shana had a bon fire at the beach, tuesday i forgot what we did, and today we went to the movies again. Tommorrow we're going to the museum of tolerance and then I have practice and on saturday we're doing something with my cousin.

I really can't wait till bryan leaves cause we've been fighting non stop since he got here and he's really bothering me. Plus we'll finally have the house to our selves again cause my aunt moved out YAY. We'll I have some other things I need to do. I'll try to update again soon.<b>

<b>Well yesterday my aunt acame to live with us cause she's having some problems. But that means less internet time for me cause she's alays on the phone so if anyone wants to talk to me they better call me. But the good thing about her living with us is the fact I can actuallydo more things now cause she can babysit for me.<b>

<b>Today I went to enroll for EPHS and on the form it said to be there at 7 am so we went early cause my counsler said to. When I got there the line was already all the way around the block. Then a guy came outside and said there was only 3 locations left te still had room, everyone else would be wait listed and it was even 7 yet when he told us this and I was pretty far back in the line. <b>Have you ever been in love? Horrible, isn't it? It makes you so vulnerable. It opens your chest and it opens your heart and it means someone can get inside you and mess you up. You build up all these defenses. You build up this whole armor, for years, so nothing can hurt you, then one stupid person, no different from any other stupid person, wanders into your stupid life...You give them a piece of you. They don't ask for it. They do something dumb one day like kiss you, or smile at you, and then your life isn't your own anymore. Love takes hostages. It gets inside you. It eats you out and leaves you crying in the darkness, so a simple phrase like 'maybe we should just be friends' or 'how very perceptive' turns into a glass splinter working its way into your heart. It hurts. Not just in the imagination. Not just in the mind. It's a soul-hurt, a body-hurt, a real gets-inside-you-and-rips-you-apart pain. I hate love.<b>
